# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Everything below is NOT needed to display the map on the web interface.
# The deployed site only needs:
#   index.html, css/styles.css, js/config.js, js/map.js, data/Data_regeocoded.geojson
# (Leaflet + markercluster load from CDN.) Everything else is data-processing /
# source / build tooling and is kept locally but out of the repo.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Python tooling & the offline geocoder workspace
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.py
don_geocode/

# Source / intermediate / report data (frontend loads only data/Data_regeocoded.geojson)
*.csv
ADMIN_1.geojson
ADMIN_2.geojson
ADMIN_3.geojson
errors.json
data/Data.geojson
data/Data_fixed.geojson
data/Data_settlement_fixed.geojson
data/Data_settlement_fixed.geojson.bak
data/donetsk_oblast_boundary.geojson
data/donetsk_boundaries.geojson
data/settlement_fix_report.json
data/regeocode_report.json

# Visualizations / screenshots
*.png
